Tyrael: This means that if their base is damaged, it's more likely 
that any further damages will cause them to use more ressources. We'll 
land at 50 klicks and walk the rest, because they may have air defense 
installed.

The wind was rushing in the bird's feathers. He watched closely the 
ground to find a suitable landing spot between the jungle down there.

Tyrael: There! See that small rock over there? Land there. The bogs 
around here will cover our position.

He landed and transformed to bot mode, reducing his glow to the 
minimum, as the surroundings were dark.
